relevant_findings.general: well-appearing in no acute distress, comfortable, appropriate
relevant_findings.heent: normocephalic/atraumatic, pupils equal, round, reactive to light and accommodation, extraocular movements intact, sclerae non-icteric, moist mucous membranes, oropharynx clear
relevant_findings.neck: supple, no thyromegaly, no jugular venous distention, no carotid bruits
relevant_findings.lungs: clear to auscultation bilaterally, no rubs, rhonchi, or wheezes, good air movement, respiratory effort unlabored, no accessory muscle use
relevant_findings.heart: point of maximal impulse non-displaced, regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops, normal S1-S2
relevant_findings.abdomen: normal bowel sounds, diffuse tenderness to palpation worse in right upper quadrant, no masses or hepatosplenomegaly, no rebound tenderness or guarding
relevant_findings.extremities: warm, well-perfused, no cyanosis, clubbing, or edema, 2+ peripheral pulses (radials, dorsalis pedis)
relevant_findings.lymph: no cervical, axillary, or inguinal lymphadenopathy
relevant_findings.neuro: awake, alert and oriented to person, place, and time, cranial nerves II-XII grossly intact
